dialogue.speaker: Dilbert
dialogue.text: DO YOU REALIZE THAT IF WE STAY TOGETHER FOR SEVEN YEARS, WE ARE CONSIDERED MARRIED BY COMMON LAW?

dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text: THAT MEANS I OWN HALF OF ALL YOUR WORLDLY POSSESSIONS.

dialogue.speaker: Dilbert
dialogue.text: I PLAN TO SELL MY HALF... MAYBE BUY SOME TASTEFUL THINGS INSTEAD.
